<html>
<head>
  <meta charset='utf-8' />
  <title>Queueing Failure Notification</title>
</head>

<style>
  h2 {background-color: #005ea2; color: white; padding: 5px;}
  div {border-bottom: 1px solid grey; padding:40px;}
  img {padding: 10px;}
  body {margin: 10px;}
  table {
    font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    width: 100%;
  }
  table td, table th {
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    padding: 8px;
  }
  table tr:nth-child(even){background-color: #f2f2f2;}
  table th {
    padding-top: 12px;
    padding-bottom: 12px;
    text-align: left;
    background-color: white;
    color: black;
  }
  a{padding: 5px; font-size: 1.06rem; line-height: 1.5;}
  h3{margin-top: 25px;}
</style>

<body>

<div>
  <p>
    The Emissions Collection and Monitoring Plan System (ECMPS) was unable to submit your data, identified below, to the U.S. Environmental Protection Agency (EPA). ECMPS Technical Support has been made aware of the issue and should be contacting you soon to help resolve the problem. If you do not hear from Technical Support within a reasonable amount of time, please feel free to contact the team at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a>.
  </p>

  <p>
    {{submissionType}} submission for {{facilityName}}, {{stateCode}}, Oris Code {{orisCode}}, Location ID(s) {{configuration}}. Submitted on {{submissionDateDisplay}}.
  </p>

  <p>
    ------------------------------
    <br />
    E-Signature information for this submission:
  </p>

  <p>
    If you have any questions regarding this correspondence, please contact <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a> and/or your EPA Monitoring/Emissions Reporting analyst. For analyst contact information, see <a href="{{cdxUrl}}">CAMD Staff Contacts.</a>
  </p>
  <p>
    To: {{toEmail}}
  </p>
  <p>
    CC: {{ccEmail}}
  </p>

  <p>
    <strong>Error Details:</strong>
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>Error Reference ID:</strong> {{errorId}}
  </p>
  <pre class="error-details">{{errorDetails}}</pre>

</div>

</body>
</html>
